<view class="page">
  <view class="header">
    <view class="logo">🎱</view>
    <view class="title">福彩助手</view>
    <view class="version">v1.0.0</view>
  </view>
  
  <view class="content card" wx:if="{{content}}">
    <rich-text nodes="{{content}}"></rich-text>
  </view>
  
  <view class="content card" wx:else>
    <view class="intro">
      <text class="intro-text">
        福彩助手是一款专业的福彩查询应用，为您提供最新、最准确的福彩开奖信息查询服务。
      </text>
    </view>
    
    <view class="features">
      <view class="feature-item">
        <view class="feature-icon">📋</view>
        <view class="feature-text">
          <view class="feature-title">开奖查询</view>
          <view class="feature-desc">支持双色球、七乐彩、22选5、3D、快乐8等多种福彩开奖查询</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      
      <view class="feature-item">
        <view class="feature-icon">📍</view>
        <view class="feature-text">
          <view class="feature-title">站点查询</view>
          <view class="feature-desc">附近彩票站点一键查询，导航直达</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      
      <view class="feature-item">
        <view class="feature-icon">📰</view>
        <view class="feature-text">
          <view class="feature-title">新闻资讯</view>
          <view class="feature-desc">最新中奖信息、福彩动态及时推送</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    
    <view class="contact">
      <view class="contact-title">联系我们</view>
      <view class="contact-item">
        <text>客服电话：400-xxx-xxxx</text>
      </view>
      <view class="contact-item">
        <text>工作时间：9:00 - 18:00</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  
  <view class="footer">
    <text class="copyright">© 2024 福彩助手</text>
    <text class="disclaimer">本应用仅供参考，开奖信息以官方公布为准</text>
  </view>
</view>
